00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:58,600
Fucker!

574
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:13,160
Gotta call Kincaid.

575
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:22,040
Dewey, where is everybody?

576
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:29,280
- Oh, God.
-Jennifer?

577
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:32,840
Angelina?
Tom?

578
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:37,360
Oh, my God!
What happened?

579
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:42,880
Don't do that.
I'm overreacting.

580
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:46,760
Dewdrop?

581
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:55,120
- Stone?
- Oh, my God!

582
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:57,600
Oh, God, Stone!

583
00:41:57,840 --> 00:42:00,960
Oh, God!

584
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:09,160
- Dewey, is he dead?
- Yeah.

585
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:13,320
Everyone back inside!

586
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:18,920
It's all right.
Don't panic.

587
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:23,160
